			17 March 2009 at 08:02</a>		</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

		<p>One the whole I find Word OK, BUT there&#8217;s always been something that bugs me in every version and I can&#8217;t believe that I&#8217;m the only one that gets so frustrated by it.</p>
<p>Section breaks and formatting f**king sucks!!!</p>
<p>It&#8217;s the two lines either side of a section break.  Somehow the formatting is unavoidably linked, so the last line of a previous section HAS to be formatted the same as the first line of the next section and it is a f**king PITA when I&#8217;m trying to get a pixel perfect document.</p>
