<p>AND, I don&#8217;t want an extra page which I can&#8217;t f**king delete at the end of my document just because the previous section is two column.  FFS!  I try to delete the last section break and &#8220;Boom&#8221; my whole f**king document goes to single column! FFS!</p>
<p>I f**king hate Word.  The only problem is I haven&#8217;t got any f**king thing better to use.  Open Office is just too &#8220;dark side&#8221; for me and, well&#8230;., f**k getting a Mac!</p>

		
